# LICENSE - OBJ to Tetrahedron Mesh Toolchain
This toolchain consists of two parts: **self-developed code** and **third-party open-source components**, each governed by different licenses as detailed below:

## 1. Self-Developed Code (MIT License)
The copyright of the following self-developed programs/code is owned by the developer and licensed under the MIT License:
- obj2ply.py / obj2ply.exe (OBJ to PLY converter)
- nodele2tet.cpp / nodele2tet.exe (NODE/ELE to TET converter)
- obj2tet.cpp / obj2tet.exe (One-click OBJ to TET workflow tool)

